cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.CY

The paper focuses on evaluating the performance of Public Safety Communication (PSC) networking and communication technologies, which falls under the category of network infrastructure and security (cs.NI) and cyber security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the implementation of mobility models for ns-3, which is a network simulator (cs.IT). The scenarios described in the paper involve coordination and awareness of first responders, which can be considered as a system (cs.SY) and the use of mmWave-based Radio Access Network (RAN) for high-traffic use cases, which can be categorized as cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
